OL,3,CThree charged with rape in historical
OL,4,Csexual exploitation probe
OL,6,FThree men have been charged with rape
OL,7,Ffollowing an investigation into
OL,8,Fhistorical child sexual exploitation.
OL,10,FThe accused, who are all British
OL,11,FPakistanis, are said to have committed
OL,12,Foffences in Bury, Greater Manchester,
OL,13,Fbetween 1996 and 2003 against 10 girls
OL,14,Fwho were then aged between 12 and 16.
OL,16,FAshfaq Khan, 46, of Bury has been
OL,17,Fcharged with 36 counts including
OL,18,Fallegations of rape, attempted rape,
OL,19,Findecent assault and false
OL,20,Fimprisonment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
