OL,3,CThree charged with rape in historical
OL,4,Csexual exploitation probe
OL,6,FZaheer Iqbal, 52, of Accrington,
OL,7,FLancashire, has been charged with four
OL,8,Fcounts of rape and two counts of false
OL,9,Fimprisonment.
OL,11,FQamar Jehangeer, 38, of Bolton,
OL,12,FGreater Manchester, is accused of four
OL,13,Fcounts of rape.
OL,15,FThe charges follow the launch of
OL,16,FOperation Sky, a "complex and
OL,17,Fsensitive" investigation focused on
OL,18,Fthe town.
