OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784634473
OL,3,CThree charged with rape in historical
OL,4,Csexual exploitation probe
OL,6,FIn a statement, Greater Manchester
OL,7,FPolice said: "Officers are working
OL,8,Fwith trauma-informed support services
OL,9,Fto safeguard and support all those
OL,10,Fthat have been affected.
OL,12,F"They continue to work at length to
OL,13,Fensure their safety and well-being is
OL,14,Fthe number one priority."
OL,16,FThe defendants will appear at
OL,17,FManchester Magistrates' Court on 22
OL,18,FJuly, police said.
